poll <- c(64.0, 7.3, 28.7)
names(poll) <- c("", "", "")
#>     .     
pos <- cumsum(poll) - poll / 2
x_text <- 0.75 * cos(pi / 2 - (2 * pi) * pos / 100)
y_text <- 0.75 * sin(pi / 2 - (2 * pi) * pos / 100)
